pull_request.title: Fixes multiple switches
pull_request.body: Using `select` only the first switch section is ever selected, using `selectAll` fixes this and allows multiple switches.

pull_request.title: Acorn update, fixes spread operator in object literal
pull_request.body:
Fixes #275.

- Updates acorn to 5.4.1
- Updates ecmaVersion to 9

This is similar to this PR for rollup https://github.com/rollup/rollup/pull/1953
